## Resource Loading and Management in C++

```cpp
#include "loader/ResourceLoader.h"
#include "loader/cache/CachedResource.h"

void loadResource(const std::string& url) {
    ResourceLoader loader;
    loader.load(url);
}

void cacheResource(const std::string& url) {
    CachedResource cached;
    // ... logic to cache resource ...
}
```

